data.description: Great for the 1st time buyer of someone downsizing. Hardwood floors in  large living room with wood burning stove insert. 2021 carpet in 3 bedrooms and  waterproof laminate flooring in kitchen and dining area Oversized laundry room with storage, Great corner coffee bar in kitchen with large3 glass door to look outside on 1.5 acres and large deck. Large circular driveway with 2 car garage. HVAC new in 3/2021, Sump pump 2019, Roof 2017, HWT 2017 and new septic in 2017. Vapor barrier and additional insulation 2017. House is well cared for ready for a new family to enjoy. Great views across the street. Electrical has been added to left of house for a shop or camper. Very comfortable country living but so close to Cabot, Jacksonville and back gate of LRAFB, Being sold as is. Sq. Ft. approximate, measuring encouraged.
